ms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106538281.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKaran%20Johar%20is%20set%20to%20roll%20out%20the%20third%20installment%20of%20the%20'Dulhania'%20franchise%2C%20and%20Janhvi%20Kapoor%20is%20rumored%20to%20replace%20Alia%20Bhatt%20opposite%20Varun%20Dhawan.%20The%20film%2C%20directed%20by%20Shashank%20Khaitan%2C%20will%20feature%20a%20new%20storyline%20and%20characters.%20Janhvi%2C%20with%20multiple%20projects%2C%20will%20make%20her%20debut%20in%20the%20popular%20franchise.%20The%20shooting%20begins%20after%20Varun%20completes%20'Theri'%20remake.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B2-Year%20Probe%20-%20Why%20Summons%20Just%20Before%20Polls%3F%26quot%3B%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Slams%20BJP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20claims%20by%20his%20party%20of%20his%20possible%20arrest%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20today%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20Chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20alleged%20that%20summons%20were%20issued%20to%20him%20so%20that%20he%20cannot%20campaign%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20He%20said%20no%20corruption%20had%20taken%20place%20in%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%20case%20and%20reiterated%20his%20party's%20claims%20that%20the%20BJP%20is%20trying%20to%20arrest%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20must%20have%20heard%20about%20the%20liquor%20policy%20scam%20several%20times%20in%20the%20past%20two%20years.%20In%20these%20two%20years%2C%20all%20of%20the%20BJP's%20agencies%20have%20carried%20out%20several%20raids%20and%20arrested%20several%20people%2C%20but%20they%20haven't%20been%20able%20to%20find%20corruption%20amounting%20to%20even%20a%20single%20paisa.%20If%20there%20has%20actually%20been%20corruption%2C%20where%20have%20all%20the%20crores%20gone%3F%20Has%20all%20the%20money%20vanished%20into%20thin%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20asked%20in%20Hindi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal%20claimed%20that%20no%20corruption%20had%20taken%20place%20at%20all%2C%20and%20pointed%20out%20that%20money%20would%20have%20been%20found%20if%20that%20hadn't%20been%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20out%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20the%20AAP%20chief%2C%20who%20has%20skipped%20three%20summons%20issued%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20jailed%20several%20AAP%20leaders%20in%20this%20fictitious%20case.%20There%20is%20no%20evidence%20against%20anyone%20and%20nothing%20is%20being%20proven...%20They%20are%20just%20putting%20anyone%20in%20jail.%20Now%20the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20arrest%20me.%20My%20biggest%20asset%20is%20my%20honesty%20and%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20tarnish%20my%20reputation%20by%20levelling%20false%20allegations%20and%20issuing%20baseless%20summons.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20lawyers%20have%20told%20me%20that%20the%20summons%20are%20illegal%2C%20and%20I%20have%20laid%20out%20the%20reasons%20for%20this%20in%20detail%20in%20letters%20to%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate.%20But%20they%20have%20not%20responded%20to%20a%20single%20reason%2C%20indicating%20that%20they%20don't%20have%20any%20answers%E2%80%A6%20The%20BJP's%20intent%20is%20not%20investigation%2C%20they%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20I%20cannot%20campaign%20for%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20The%20investigation%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20two%20years%20but%20they%20have%20summoned%20me%20right%20before%20the%20elections.%20Why%20didn't%20they%20summon%20me%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20out%20that%20he%20had%20appeared%20before%20the%20CBI%20when%20the%20agency%20had%20summoned%20him%20eight%20months%20ago%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%20the%20notice%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20two%20months%20before%20the%20elections%20indicates%20that%20the%20BJP%20wants%20to%20get%20him%20arrested%20in%20the%20guise%20of%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Trying%20To%20Break%20Up%20Parties'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERepeating%20an%20allegation%20made%20several%20times%20by%20his%20party%20and%20its%20allies%20in%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20the%20AAP%20chief%20said%20the%20ruling%20party%20is%20not%20going%20after%20the%20corrupt%20but%20simply%20trying%20to%20break%20up%20parties%20using%20central%20agencies%20so%20that%20it%20can%20get%20their%20leaders%20to%20join%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20several%20instances%20of%20leaders%20of%20opposition%20parties%20facing%20cases%20by%20Central%20agencies%20or%20serious%20allegations%20which%20are%20then%20closed%20or%20put%20in%20cold%20storage%20when%20they%20join%20the%20BJP...%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%20and%20Vijay%20Nair%20are%20not%20in%20jail%20because%20they%20indulged%20in%20corruption%2C%20but%20because%20they%20refused%20to%20join%20the%20BJP%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20country%20can't%20progress%20if%20they%20put%20honest%20leaders%20in%20jail%20and%20induct%20the%20corrupt%20into%20their%20party...%20This%20is%20wrong%20for%20our%20democracy.%20We%20need%20to%20stop%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704353640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F33ksre98_arvind-kejriwal-presser-650-_650x400_04_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-corruption-where-did-the-crores-go-arvind-kejriwal-on-delhi-liquor-policy-probe-4797721%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20claims%20by%20his%20party%20of%20his%20possible%20arrest%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20today%2C%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20Chief%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20has%20alleged%20that%20summons%20were%20issued%20to%20him%20so%20that%20he%20ca