2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Eanes%20first%20met%20Kelce%20through%20Kelce's%20college%20roommate%20and%20always%20thought%20he%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20be%20a%20huge%20star.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20always%20the%20life%20of%20the%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20Andr%C3%A9%20told%20the%20Times.%20%26quot%3BEveryone%20wanted%20to%20go%20hang%20out%20with%20Travis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%202015%20Complex%20magazine%20feature%2C%20Kelce%20was%20offered%20a%20chance%20to%20star%20in%20his%20own%20reality%20dating%20show%2C%20per%20the%20Times.%20While%20his%20managers%20were%20initially%20reluctant%2C%20they%20eventually%20changed%20their%20minds%20when%20they%20considered%20how%20it%20might%20raise%20the%20NFL%20star's%20profile.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20aside%2C%20the%20Eanes%20also%20secured%20endorsement%20deals%20for%20Kelce%20with%20companies%20not%20traditionally%20affiliated%20with%20the%20NFL%20%E2%80%94%20enabling%20him%20to%20build%20his%20brand%20outside%20football%2C%20per%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Kelce's%20Super%20Bowl%20win%20in%20March%20last%20year%2C%20%26quot%3BSaturday%20Night%20Live%26quot%3B%20came%20calling%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%2034-year-old%20was%20finally%20able%20to%20fulfill%20his%20childhood%20dream%20of%20hosting%20the%20show%2C%20the%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20that%2C%20Kelce's%20star%20began%20to%20rise%20as%20planned%2C%20but%20there%20was%20one%20thing%20that%20happened%20last%20year%20that%20his%20managers%20couldn't%20have%20anticipated%20%E2%80%94%20him%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ftaylor-swift-travis-kelce-relationship-timeline-photos-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edating%20Taylor%20Swift%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20per%20the%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20positioned%20Travis%20to%20be%20world%20famous%2C%26quot%3B%20Andr%C3%A9%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20didn't%20know%20how%20it%20would%20happen%2C%20or%20when%20it%20would%20happen%2C%20or%20what%20would%20h