as%20conceptualised%20as%20a%20mechanism%20to%20provide%20primary%20healthcare%20accessible%20to%20communities%20in%20Delhi%20at%20their%20doorstep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20hyperlocal%20clinics%20cater%20to%20the%20needs%20of%20not%20only%20the%20population%20of%20Delhi%20but%20also%20migratory%20and%20floating%20population%20from%20neighbouring%20states%2C%20which%20makes%20for%20a%20considerable%20patient%20load.%20There%20are%20also%20many%20areas%2C%20particularly%20slums%2C%20where%20the%20poor%20do%20not%20get%20easily%20get%20primary%20healthcare.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704351420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-03%2Faam-aadmi-mohalla-clinic-650_650x400_51489764972.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Flieutenant-governor-vk-saxena-asks-cbi-to-investigate-delhi-mohalla-clinic-fake-tests-scam-4797826%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Delhi%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20has%20asked%20the%20CBI%20to%20investigate%20corruption%20allegations%20in%20diagnostic%20tests%20done%20at%20Delhi's%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Mohalla%20Clinics%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Flieutenant-governor-vk-saxena-asks-cbi-to-investigate-delhi-mohalla-clinic-fake-tests-scam-4797826%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Flieutenant-governor-vk-saxena-asks-cbi-to-investigate-delhi-mohalla-clinic-fake-tests-scam-4797826%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fdelhi-news%2Flieutenant-governor-vk-saxena-asks-cbi-to-investigate-delhi-mohalla-clinic-fake-tests-scam-4797826%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22ICC%20introduces%20changes%20to%20DRS%20protocols%2C%20concussion%20rules%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704351342000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106536851%2Cimgsize-14202.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Ficc-introduces-changes-to-drs-protocols-concussion-replacement-rules%2Farticleshow%2F106536826.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20has%20made%20significant%20changes%20to%20its%20Decision%20Review%20System%20(DRS)%20protocols%20and%20concussion%20replacement%20rules%2C%20effective%20from%20December%2012%2C%202023.%20The%20changes%20aim%20to%20improve%20clarity%20and%20fairness%20in%20the%20decision-making%20process%2C%20particularly%20in%20stumping%20reviews.%20Umpires%20will%20now%20assess%20side-on%20replays%20for%20stumping%20without%20considering%20caught-behind%20scenarios%20during%20DRS%20referrals%20by%20the%20teams.%20Teams%20wishing%20to%20refer%20to%20a%20caught-behind%20appeal%20along%20with%20stumping%20must%20use%20a%20separate%20DRS%20option.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Ficc-introduces-changes-to-drs-protocols-concussion-replacement-rules%2Farticleshow%2F106536826.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Woman%20Takes%20Revenge%20On%20Cheating%20Boyfriend%2C%20Reports%20Him%20For%20Unpaid%20Taxes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20is%20going%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20for%20sharing%20here%20innovative%20revenge%20plot%20against%20cheating%20boyfriend.%20Ava%20Louise%2C%20an%20OnlyFans%20model%2C%20posted%20a%20video%20on%20TikTok%20in%20which%20she%20claimed%20she%20reported%20the%20man%20to%20the%20Internal%20Revenue%20Service%20(IRS)%20of%20the%20United%20States%20government%20for%20unpaid%20taxes.%20According%20to%20%3Cem%3EDistractify%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20video%20she%20posted%20has%20gone%20massively%20viral%2C%20amassing%20over%203.8%20million%20views.%20It%20appears%20that%20Ms%20Louise%20fulfilled%20the%20conditions%20mentioned%20on%20the%20IRS%20website%20to%20receive%20the%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.distractify.com%2Fp%2Fwoman-reports-ex-to-irs-for-reward-money%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDistractify%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20OnlyFans%20model%20said%20in%20the%20video%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20ex%20confided%20in%20me%20he%20never%20paid%20his%20taxes%2C%20then%20cheated%20on%20me%20a%20few%20months%20later%20I%20reported%20him%20to%20the%20IRS%20and%20collected%20over%20100k%20in%20reward%20money.%20I'm%20spending%20his%20money%20daily%20while%20he's%20facing%20years%20in%20jail.%20The%20female%20rage%20is%20a%20powerful%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20claim%20shared%20by%20Ms%20Louise%2C%20she%20pocketed%20around%20Rs%2083%20lakh%20by%20reporting%20her%20ex-boyfriend%20for%20unpaid%20taxes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20IRS%20whistleblower%20programme%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoing%20by%20Ms%20Louise's%20account%2C%20she%20appears%20to%20have%20made%20use%20of%20the%20whistleblower%20programme%20of%20the%20agency%20that%20is%20responsible%20for%20collecting%20taxes%20and%20enforcing%20tax%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fcompliance%2Fwhistleblower-office%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20IRS%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Whistleblower%20Office%20pays%20monetary%20awards%20to%20eligible%20individuals%20whose%20information%20is%20used%20by%20the%20agency.%20%26quot%3BThe%20award%20percentage%20depends%20on%20several%20factors%2C%20but%20generally%20falls%20between%2015%20and%2030%20percent%20of%20the%20proceeds%20collected%20and%20attributable%20to%20the%20whistleblower's%20information%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20further%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20become%20eligible%2C%20a%20person%20has%20to%20submit%20a%20claim%20of%20non-compliance%20exceeding%20over%20%242%2C000%2C000%20by%20an%20individual.%20Further%2C%20the%20accused%20should%20have%20a%20gross%20annual%20income%20of%20over%20%24200%2C000%20%26quot%3Bfor%20at%20least%20one%20of%20the%20tax%20years%20in%20question%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20such%20an%20incident%20has%20gone%20viral%20on%20social%20media.%20In%20June%202023%2C%20three%20women%20in%20China%20teamed%20up%20to%20expose%20a%20man%20who%20posed%20as%20a%20love%20interest%20and%20cheated%20them%20of%20100%2C000%20yuan%20(Rs%2011%2C67%2C982).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20South%20China%20Morning%20Post%20(SCMP)%2C%20the%20Shanghai%20man%20has%20received%20two%20years%20and%20six%20months%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20year%20before%20that%2C%20a%20woman%20in%20the%20US%20tracked%20her%20cheating%20boyfriend%20using%20Apple's%20AirTag%20and%20ran%20over%20him%20with%20a%20car%20in%20front%20of%20a%20bar.%20She%20was%20arrested%20and%20charged%20with%20murder.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704351300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F9j49e3v_ava-louise_625x300_04_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-takes-revenge-on-cheating-boyfriend-by-reporting-him-for-unpaid-taxes-4797815%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20TikTok%20video%20where%20Ava%20Louise%20shared%20her%20story%20has%20amassed%20more%20than%203.8%20million%20views.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-takes-revenge-on-cheating-boyfriend-by-reporting-him-for-unpaid-taxes-4797815%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-takes-revenge-on-cheating-boyfriend-by-reporting-him-for-unpaid-taxes-4797815%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwoman-takes-revenge-on-cheating-boyfriend-by-reporting-him-for-unpaid-taxes-4797815%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Supreme%20Court%20Dismisses%20Petition%20Of%20Indian%20Arrested%20In%20US%20Murder%20Plot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDismissing%20the%20petition%20filed%20on%20behalf%20of%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20who%20has%20been%20accused%20by%20the%20United%20States%20of%20conspiring%20to%20kill%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20that%20the%20matter%20pertains%20to%20international%20law%20and%20it%20must%20respect%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20courts%20in%20other%20countries.%20The%20court%20also%20said%20it%20cannot%20interfere%20because%20the%20matter%20is%20a%20sensitive%20one%20and%20has%20international%20implications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta%20is%20in%20prison%20in%20Prague%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20and%20the%20United%20States%20has%20sought%20his%20extradition%20for%20his%20alleged%20involvement%20in%20a%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20%26quot%3Bmurder%20for%20hire%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHearing%20the%20petition%20filed%20by%20one%20of%20Mr%20Gupta's%20family%20members%20seeking%20instructions%20being%20given%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20for%20appropriate%20diplomatic%20help%20-%20including%20consular%20access%20and%20legal%20aid%20-%20Justice%20Sanjiv%20Khanna%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20outset%20itself%2C%20we%20wish%20to%20say%20we%20don't%20think%20we%20can%20do%20anything%20in%20this%20regard%20or%20give%20any%20relief.%20The%20only%20intervention%20we%20can%20look%20into%20is%20consular%20access%20as%20per%20Vienna%20Convention%2C%20which%20you%20yourself%20say%20in%20the%20petition%20that%20you%20have%20got.%20The%20matter%20pertains%20to%20international%20law%2C%20we%20have%20to%20respect%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%20courts%20in%20foreign%20countries.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAppearing%20for%20the%20petitioner%2C%20Senior%20Advocate%20CA%20Sundaram%20said%2C%20%26quot%3B(Give)%20at%20least%20some%20direction%20to%20the%20ministries.%20He%20(Nikhil%20Gupta)%20shouldn't%20have%20been%20in%20the%20country%20at%20all.%20He%20has%20not%20got%20consular%20access.%20Petition%20has%20been%20wrongly%20interpreted.%20I%20have%20been%20given%20the%20extradition%20order%20yesterday...%20Legal%20assistance%20is%20all%20I%20am%20asking.%20An%20interpreter%20and%20translator%20also.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20for%20the%20government%20to%20decide.%20If%20the%20petitioner%20wants%20to%20approach%20the%20government%2C%20the%20Centre%20may%20take%20it%20as%20a%20representation%20from%20the%20petitioner.%20It%20is%20a%20sensitive%20matter%20for%20the%20government%20also%20as%20it%20has%20international%20ramifications.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sundaram%20pointed%20out%20that%20Mr%20Gupta%20has%20been%20kept%20in%20solitary%20confinement%20and%20that%20he%20needs%20the%20ministry's%20help%20to%20defend%20himself.%20The%20court%2C%20however%2C%20denied%20relief%20and%20dismissed%20the%20petition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20previous%20hearing%20on%20December%2015%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20asked%20Mr%20Gupta's%20family%20to%20approach%20a%20court%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic.%20Even%20in%20that%20hearing%2C%20it%20had%20made%20the%20point%20that%20this%20was%20an%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20sensitive%20matter%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Petition%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20petition%2C%20Nikhil%20Gupta%20was%20in%20the%20Czech%20Republic%20on%20a%20business%20trip%20when%20he%20was%20illegally%20detained%20at%20Prague%20Airport%20on%20June%2030.%20It%20states%20that%20there%20were%20irregularities%20in%20his%20arrest%20and%20no%20formal%20arrest%20warrant%20was%20produced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20claims%20that%20consular%20access%20to%20Mr%20Gupta%20has%20not%20been%20granted%20and%20he%20has%20also%20not%20been%20given%20the%20right%20to%20contact%20his%20family%20in%20India%20or%20seek%20legal%20representation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllegations%20of%20torture%20have%20also%20been%20made%2C%20and%20the%20petition%20states%20that%20Mr%20Gupta%20faces%20a%20threat%20to%20his%20life%20because%20he%20is%20locked%20in%20a%20prison%20in%20a%20foreign%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Got%20Access%20Thrice'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20had%20said%20last%20month%20that%20India%20had%20got%20consular%20access%20to%20Mr%20Gupta%20on%20at%20least%20three%20occasions%20and%20is%20extending%20the%20necessary%20assistance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Department%20of%20Justice%20has%20charged%20Mr%20Gupta%20with%20conspiring%20with%20an%20Indian%20government%20official%20to%20assassinate%20Pannun%20on%20American%20soil.%20The%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20holds%20citizenship%20of%20both%20the%20US%20and%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Gupta%20is%20accused%20of%20attempting%20to%20hire%20a%20hitman%2C%20who%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20an%20undercover%20US%20federal%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704351120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fc9cdh8ao_us-prison-generic-us-jail-generic-getty_625x300_24_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finternational-ramifications-supreme-court-dismisses-petition-of-indian-arrested-in-us-murder-plot-4797725%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dismissing%20the%20petition%20filed%20on%20behalf%20of%20Nikhil%20Gupta%2C%20who%20has%20been%20accused%20by%20the%20US%20of%20conspiring%20to%20kill%20Khalistani%20terrorist%20Gurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20said%20that%20it%20must%20respect%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20courts%20in%20other%20countries.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Finternational-ramifications-supreme-court-dismisses-petition-of-indian-arrested-in-us-murder-plot-4797725%22%2C%22cdnA