n%20Hollywood%20and%20in%20India%2C%20have%20shown%20characters%20crossing%20hurdles%2C%20successfully%20overcoming%20life-threatening%20challenges%20to%20reach%20their%20goal.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20park%20in%20the%20United%20States%20where%20visitors%20can%20find%20real%20diamonds%20in%20their%20volcanic%20state.%20It%20is%20known%20as%20the%20Diamonds%20State%20park%20and%20is%20located%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Arkansas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202023%2C%20a%20man%20from%20Arkansas%20found%20a%204.87-carat%20diamond.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F12%2F24%2Fus%2Farkansas-diamond-park-discovery-trnd%2Findex.html%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jerry%20Evans%20visited%20the%20park%20with%20his%20girlfriend%20in%20spring%20and%20picked%20up%20what%20he%20thought%20was%20a%20piece%20of%20glass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20he%20pocketed%20the%20pyramid-shaped%20find%2C%20he%20wasn't%20sure%20if%20it%20was%20a%20diamond%2C%20Evans%20said%20in%20a%20news%20release%20posted%20on%20the%20park's%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20so%20clear.%20I%20really%20didn't%20know.%20We%20were%20picking%20up%20everything%20thinking%20it%20was%20a%20diamond%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Evans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20reaching%20home%2C%20he%20sent%20the%20jelly%20bean-sized%20object%20to%20Gemological%20Institute%20of%20America%20that%20informed%20him%20he%20had%20found%20a%20near-colourless%20diamond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20they%20called%20and%20told%20me%20it%20was%20real%2C%20I%20was%20tickled%20to%20death!%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Evans'%20diamond%20became%20the%20largest%20one%20registered%20at%20the%20park%20since%20Labour%20Day%20of%202020%2C%20when%20Kevin%20Kinard%20of%20Maumelle%2C%20Arkansas%2C%20found%20a%209.07-carat%20brown%20diamond%20there%2C%20according%20to%20park%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20known%20as%20Crater%20of%20Diamon