%2066%20Test%20matches%2C%20as%20well%20as%20most%20of%20his%20domestic%20career%2C%20at%20Newlands%20and%20is%20currently%20coach%20of%20Western%20Province%2C%20based%20at%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20batsman%20you%20don't%20mind%20pace%20in%20the%20wicket%20if%20the%20bounce%20is%20consistent%20but%20the%20bounce%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20inconsistent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20expect%20a%20bit%20of%20seam%20movement%20on%20day%20one%20but%20seam%20movement%20with%20inconsistent%20bounce%20is%20a%20different%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSometimes%20it%20happens%20that%20a%20great%20bowling%20line-up%20bowls%20out%20a%20team%20cheaply%20but%20if%20both%20batting%20line-ups%20can't%20bat%20there's%20something%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrince%20said%20the%20conditions%20had%20taken%20South%20Africa%20by%20surprise%2C%20prompting%20them%20to%20bat%20in%20bright%20sunshine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20grass%20on%20the%20pitch%20but%20the%20tendency%20at%20Newlands%20is%20for%20it%20to%20take%20spin%20later%20on%20so%20it%20made%20sense%20to%20bat.%20I%20don't%20think%20anyone%20could%20have%20foreseen%20how%20the%20pitch%20would%20play.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Siraj%20stars%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiraj%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20said%20maintaining%20control%20was%20crucial%20on%20a%20pitch%20which%20assisted%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20good%20communication%20from%20the%20wicketkeeper%20(%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22KL%20Rahul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1688-lokesh-rahul-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKL%20Rahul%3C%2Fa%3E)%20about%20the%20right%20lengths%20to%20bowl%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Siraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa's%20first%20innings%20total%20was%20their%20lowest%20in%20almost%2092%20years%2C%20since%20they%20were%20bowled%20out%20for%2036%20and%2045%20by%20Australia%20on%20a%20r