3BLord%20Ram%20was%20a%20non-vegetarian%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Awhad%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20camp%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20made%20the%20comment%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Shridi%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLord%20Ram%20belongs%20to%20us%2C%20Bahujans.%20He%20used%20to%20hunt%20and%20eat%20animals.%20He%20is%20a%20Bahujan.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20make%20everyone%20a%20vegetarian%20by%20giving%20Lord%20Ram's%20example.%20But%20Lord%20Ram%20was%20not%20a%20vegetarian%2C%20he%20was%20a%20non-vegetarian.%20A%20person%20who%20has%20stayed%20in%20the%20forest%20for%2014%20years%20-%20where%20will%20he%20go%20to%20find%20vegetarian%20food%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Awhad%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20years%20Lord%20Ram%20spent%20in%20the%20forests%20in%20the%20Hindu%20epic%20Ramayana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20comment%2C%20which%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the%20grand%20consecration%20of%20the%20new%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Ayodhya%20later%20this%20month%2C%20has%20sparked%20a%20massive%20controversy%2C%20with%20some%20seeking%20action%20against%20him%20for%20hurting%20religious%20sentiments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20group%20of%20supporters%20of%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%20turned%20up%20outside%20Mr%20Awhad's%20Mumbai%20home%20on%20Wednesday%20night%20and%20shouted%20slogans%20against%20him.%20The%20protesters%20returned%20this%20morning%20with%20a%20poster%20of%20Mr%20Awhad%2C%20which%20they%20repeatedly%20hit%20with%20slippers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20have%20deployed%20extra%20personnel%20in%20front%20of%20Mr%20Awhad's%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELed%20by%20BJP%20MLA%20Ram%20Kadam%2C%20the%20protesters%20said%20they%20will%20march%20to%20the%20nearest%20police%20station%20and%20file%20a%20case%20against%20the%20NCP%20MLA%20over%20his%20comments%20that%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20of%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20devotees%20of%20Lord%20Ram%20will%20file%20a%20police%20case%20against%20Jitendra%20Awhad%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kadam%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20Balasaheb%20were%20alive%2C%20today's%20Saamana%20newspaper%20would%20have%20spoken%20harshly%20to%20those%20who%20called%20Lord%20Ram%20a%20non-vegetarian%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kadam%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Shiv%20Sena's%20mouthpiece.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20what%20is%20the%20reality%20today%3F%20Anyone%20can%20say%20anything%20about%20Lord%20Ram%3B%20anyone%20can%20make%20fun%20of%20Hindus.%20They%20don't%20care.%20They%20are%20as%20cold%20as%20ice.%20But%20come%20elections%2C%20they%20will%20talk%20about%20Hindutva%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20MLA%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Awhad%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20stop%20at%20Lord%20Ram.%20He%20pressed%20on%20and%20opened%20another%20controversy%20with%20his%20comment%20that%20India%20got%20independence%20only%20because%20of%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20and%20Jawaharlal%20Nehru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20matter%20what%20someone%20says%2C%20the%20truth%20is%20that%20we%20got%20independence%20only%20because%20of%20Gandhi%20and%20Nehru.%20Gandhi%20ji%20was%20not%20assassinated%20in%201947%2C%20but%20the%20first%20attack%20on%20him%20took%20place%20in%201935%2C%20the%20second%20in%201938%2C%20and%20the%20third%20in%201942%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Awhad%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20all%2C%20why%20did%20they%20attack%20him%20so%20many%20times...%20because%20Gandhi%20ji%20was%20a%20tradesman%20and%20an%20OBC%20(Other%20Backward%20Classes).%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20leader%20of%20such%20a%20big%20independence%20movement%20was%20an%20OBC%20was%20not%20acceptable%20to%20them%20(RSS)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MLA%20of%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20NCP%20faction%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20BJP's%20ideological%20mentor%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%20(RSS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Ayodhya%2C%20the%20local%20authorities%20and%20the%20police%20are%20