ented%20effort%20in%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20absence%20to%20consolidate%20party%20rank%20and%20file.%20More%20importantly%2C%20it%20was%20a%20visible%20instance%20of%20how%20a%20leader%20is%20born%2C%20through%20sheer%20hard%20work%20and%20persistence%2C%20and%20accepted%20by%20people%20as%20one%20of%20their%20own.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20caught%20up%20with%20Lokesh%20on%20December%2018%2C%20two%20days%20before%20it%20culminated%20in%20Visakhapatnam%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20Naidu%20and%20his%20ally%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20of%20the%20Jana%20Sena%20party.%20As%20the%20nation%20gears%20up%20for%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20Lokesh%20had%20clear%20answers%20about%20his%20party%E2%80%99s%20role%2C%20his%20own%20plan%2C%20rumours%20about%20the%20TDP%20joining%20the%20NDA%20ranks%20again%2C%20and%20why%20he%20thinks%20Naidu%E2%80%99s%20victory%20in%20the%20upcoming%20assembly%20polls%20is%20almost%20certain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHere%20is%20an%20excerpt%20from%20the%20interview%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOne%20gets%20an%20impression%20that%20while%20TDP%E2%80%99s%20governance%20centred%20around%20infrastructure%20development%2C%20YSR%20Congress%20has%20a%20focussed%20approach%20towards%20welfare%20of%20the%20poor.%20How%20do%20you%20differentiate%20between%20your%20party%20and%20Jagan%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20balance%20has%20always%20been%20between%20welfare%20and%20development.%20The%20development%20wheel%20in%20the%20cycle%20sort%20of%20loomed%20the%20welfare%20wheel.%20And%20if%20you%20look%20at%20our%20manifesto%20also%2C%20we%20have%20said%20that%20we%20will%20create%2020%20lakh%20jobs%20for%20the%20youth.%20So%20if%20you%20have%20to%20create%2020%20lakh%20jobs%2C%20and%20as%20and%20when%20we%20create%2020%20lakh%20jobs%2C%20Andhra%E2%80%99s%20economy%20will%20triple.%20So%2C%20based%20on%20the%20past%2C%20every%20six%20lakh%20jobs%20doubles%20the%20economic%20growth.%20That%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20work%20that%20we%20want%20to%20do.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20number%20of%20companies%20that%20have%20come%20to%20our%20state%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20development%20that%20has%20happened%2C%20our%20reforms%2C%20all%20that%20was%20done%20by%20Mr.%20Naidu.%20But%20we%20also%20believe%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20balanced%20by%20welfare.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20this%20government%20has%20specifically%20done%20is%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20have%20done%20welfare%20on%20the%20back%20of%20debt%20and%20that%20has%20resulted%20in%20substantial%20increase%20in%20cost%20of%20living%2C%20current%20prices%20have%20gone%20up%20nine%20times%2C%20power%20prices%20up%20by%20nine%20times.%20Petrol%2C%20diesel%20prices%20are%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20country.%20Welfare%20based%20on%20debt%20money%20is%20a%20wrong%20approach.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAndhra%20is%20in%20that%20(debt)%20trap%20and%20people%20have%20recognised%20that.%20So%20that%E2%80%99s%20something%20that%20we%20will%20break%2C%20we%20will%20break%20that%20cycle.%20We%E2%80%99ll%20put%20the%20state%20back%20on%20the%20development%20platform.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnaidus-arrest-what-is-the-andhra-pradesh-skill-development-scam%5C%22%3ETDP%20Sets%20Up%20Website%20to%20Counter%20Skill%20Development%20Scheme%20Charges%2C%20Highlights%20Praise%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThis%20(%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3Epadyatra%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3E)%20song%20that%20I%20was%20just%20listening%20to%20named%20the%20chief%20minister%20as%20%E2%80%98the%20psycho.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20chief%20minister%2C%20once%20he%20comes%20into%20power%2C%20would%20always%20like%20to%20start%20work%20on%20a%20development%20and%20welfare%20platform.%20But%20what%20he%20started%20on%20was%20the%20destruction%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eprajavedika%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20subsequently%20all%20the%20issues%20that%20he%20has%20taken%20on%20have%20just%20ruined%20the%20state.%20So%20if%20you%20look%20at%20our%20economy%2C%20power%20sector%2C%20agri-sector%2C%20mining%2C%20sand%2C%20every%20sector%20is%20ruined.%20So%2C%20people%20have%20started%20to%20call%20him%20a%20psycho.%20So%20this%20kind%20of%20psychotic%20behaviour%20will%20lead%20to%20him%20being%20called%20psycho.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20know%2C%20he%20says%20he%20has%20no%20money%20to%20make%20even%20one%20capital%20(city)%2C%20but%20he%20has%20money%20to%20do%20three%20capitals.%20How%20is%20it%20going%20to%20work%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20do%20you%20measure%20the%20success%20of%20your%20padayatra%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20if%20I%20say%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20success%2C%20you%20will%20say%2C%20obviously%20Lokesh%20will%20claim%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20success%2C%20right.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENo%2C%20but%20I%20will%20listen%20to%20you.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20will%20not%20claim%20anything.%20I%20think%20it%20is%20for%20you%20to%20judge%20whether%20Yuvagalam%20is%20a%20success%20or%20not.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrom%20my%20perspective%2C%20the%20entire%20reason%20why%20I%20started%20the%20padayatra%20is%20to%20give%20a%20platform%20for%20youth%20to%20talk%20about%20their%20problems.%20But%20then%20in%20a%20month%2C%2045%20days%20into%20the%20padayatra%2C%20you%20know%2C%20I%20realised%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20just%20youth%2C%20but%20every%20section%20of%20society%20has%20been%20troubled%20and%20this%20Yuvagalam%20has%20become%20Andhra%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Egalam%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(voice).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20manifested%20into%20the%20farmers%20talking%20about%20their%20problems%2C%20women%20talking%20about%20their%20problems%2C%20youngsters%20talking%20about%20their%20problems%2C%20students%20talking%20about%20their%20problems.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20end%2C%20you%20know%2C%20we%20realised%20that%2C%20you%20know%2C%20this%20person%20is%20just%20all%20talk%20but%20no%20work%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20something%20that%E2%80%99s%20come%20out%20now.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20look%20at%20the%20padayatra%2C%20women%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20day%2C%20have%20come%20out%2C%20volunteered%20and%20they%20stood%20there%2C%20received%20us%2C%20explained%20their%20problems%20and%2C%20you%20know%2C%20sort%20of%20also%20made%20it%20clear%20what%20they%20expect%20from%20our%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIn%20terms%20of%20social%20outreach%2C%20how%20successful%20has%20it%20been%3F%20Because%20the%20last%20time%20the%20results%20showed%20that%20the%20TDP%20had%20lost%20a%20large%20chunk%20of%20its%20traditional%20voters%20to%20this%20YSRCP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20number%20of%20seats%2C%20YSRCP%20won%20151%20and%20we%20won%2023.%20But%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20we%20got%2040%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share%20and%20YSRCP%20got%2050%25%20of%20the%20vote%20share.%20So%2C%20I%20need%20to%20convince%206%20in%20100%20to%20vote%20for%20TDP%20to%20win%20with%20a%20simple%20majority.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20has%20happened%20is%20Jagan%2C%20psycho%20Jagan%20as%20we%20fondly%20call%20him%2C%20came%20on%20a%20promise%20of%20one%20chance.%20He%20said%20he%20will%20change%20people%E2%80%99s%20lives%2C%20that%20he%20is%20his%20father%E2%80%99s%20son.%20But%20what%20people%20have%20realised%20is%20that%20their%20lives%20have%20become%20worse%20off%20and%20he%20has%20done%20nothing%20but%20ruin%20their%20lives.%20All%20the%20promises%20that%20he%20made%20for%20various%20communities%2C%20caste-wise%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20fructified.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBut%20he%20has%20five%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20from%20different%20communities.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20what%20power%20do%20they%20have%3F%20You%20know%2C%20the%20home%20minister%20is%20Dalit.%20But%20she%20cannot%20protect%20Dalits%20in%20her%20own%20constituency%20from%20YSRCP%20leaders.%20Giving%20posts%20does%20not%20change%20things%20sir%2C%20empowering%20people%20changes%20things.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%E2%80%99re%20all%20dummies.%20My%20question%20to%20Jagan%20is%20that%20why%20have%20you%20cancelled%2027%20welfare%20programmes%20of%20Dalits%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EYou%20allege%20that%20deputy%20chief%20ministers%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20power%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20I%20said%2C%20even%20the%20Dalit%20home%20minister%20is%20not%20allowed%20into%20the%20Dalit%20area%20of%20a%20village.%20She%20is%20a%20home%20minister.%20What%20can%20she%20do%20tomorrow%20then%3F%20See%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20in%20the%20state%20no%2C%20all%20the%20ministers%20are%20dummies.%20All%20the%20deputy%20CMs%20are%20dummies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20432px)%2085vw%2C%20432px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04110705%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-03-at-6.40.34-PM.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22432%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04110705%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-03-at-6.40.34-PM.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04110705%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-03-at-6.40.34-PM-225x300.jpeg%20225w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-691558%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cp%2