yatra%20%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cb%3Efrom%20the%20region%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20spent%20most%20of%20my%20time%20in%20Rayalaseema.%20The%20entire%20summer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAccess%20to%20water%20was%20a%20huge%20problem%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20been%20like%20a%20problem%20there%20since%20ever.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbsolutely.%20And%20that%20is%20what%2C%20Polavaram%20would%20have%20been%20completed.%20Water%20could%20have%20come%2C%20you%20know%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20project%20called%20Pattiseema.%20Pattiseema%20was%20a%20temporary%20project%2C%20but%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20expensive%20project.%201700%20crores%20was%20spent%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20expensive%20project.%20The%20idea%20is%20we%20will%20take%20water%20from%20Godavari%2C%20give%20it%20to%20Krishna%20Delta%2C%20from%20where%20it%20will%20be%20sent%20to%20Rayalaseema.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20whole%20idea.%20And%20Mr.%20Naidu%20worked%20on%20it%20for%20three%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20chief%20minister%2C%20simply%20because%20he%20opposed%20Pattiseema%20for%20whatever%20reason%2C%20refused%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20motors%20of%20Pattiseema.%20And%20he%20dried%20Rayalseema%20and%20dried%20Krishna%20delta.%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20in%20Rayalaseema%2C%20you%20know%2C%20despite%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20large%20number%20of%20ministers%2C%20water%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20problem.%20Lack%20of%20industrialization%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20problem.%20And%20when%20I%20walked%20in%2C%20the%20maximum%20number%20of%20my%20selfies%20came%20from%20Rayalaseema.%20That%E2%80%99s%20an%20acknowledgement%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20got%20industries%20in%20Rayalaseema.%20So%20we%20are%20proud%20of%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESo%20are%20you%20still%20calling%20for%20some%20kind%20of%20special%20category%20status%20for%20AP%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%