20CBI%2C%207%20ED.%20Rs%2043%2C000%20crores%20of%20public%20money%20was%20swindled%20by%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EI%20was%20saying%20that%20Jagan%20was%20kind%20of%20trying%20to%20put%20BJP%20in%20a%20spot%2C%20not%20TDP.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShow%20me%20one%20national%20leader%20who%20believes%20Mr.%20Naidu%20is%20corrupt.%20Just%20because%20if%20a%20madman%20falsely%20accused%20Mr.%20Naidu%2C%20manages%20all%20the%20institutions%2C%20sends%20him%20to%20judicial%20remand%20for%2053%20days%2C%20that%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20make%20him%20a%20corrupt%20politician.%20I%20mean%2C%20where%20is%20the%20proof%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20know%2C%20what%20did%20they%20say%3F%203000%20crores%20scam%20in%20skill%20development%2C%20then%20they%20said%20370%20crore.%20Now%20they%E2%80%99re%20saying%2027%20crore.%20I%20said%2C%20prove%20but%20they%E2%80%99re%20unable%20to%20prove.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%E2%80%99re%20telling%20me%20a%20man%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20minister%20for%2015%20years%2C%20spent%2015%20years%20as%20leader%20of%20opposition%20has%20indulged%20in%20a%20corruption%20scam%20worth%20only%20Rs%2027%20crores.%20We%20still%20say%20that%20the%20skill%20development%20programme%20in%20our%20government%20helped%20train%202%2C15%2C000%20kids%20and%20get%2085%2C000%20people%20jobs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20irony%20is%20that%20after%20Mr.%20Naidu%20came%20out%2C%20I%20restarted%20my%20padayatra%20in%20East%20Godavari%20where%20I%20received%20about%20six%20representations%20to%20intensify%20our%20skill%20development%20programme.%20I%20told%20them%20this%20is%20the%20reason%20Mr.%20Naidu%20was%20sent%20to%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimply%2C%20I%E2%80%99ll%20tell%20you%2C%20if%20Mr.%20Naidu%20wanted%20to%20make%20money%2C%20he%20knew%20Cyberabad%20was%20coming%20up.%20He%20knew%20the%20value%20of%20land%20in%20Hyderabad%20would%20go%20up.%20Back%20then%2C%20the%20value%20per%20acre%20was%20not%20more%20than%20a%20lakh%20of%20rupees.%20Mr.%20Naidu%20could%20have%20purchased%20a%20minimum%201%2C000%20acres.%20No%20one%20could%20have%20questioned%20that.%20He%20would%20have%20been%20worth%20nothing%20less%20than%20%24%2010-12%20billion%20dollars%20today%2C%20if%20he%20did%20that.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fpurandeswari-andhra-pradesh-bjp-chief-tdp-growth%5C%22%3EBy%20Appointing%20Purandeswari%20as%20Andhra%20Chief%2C%20Is%20BJP%20Trying%20to%20Grow%20at%20TDP%E2%80%99s%20Expense%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESimilar%20charges%20were%20filed%20against%20him%20in%20Amaravati%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20know%2C%20on%20one%20side%2C%20they%20say%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20house%20in%20Amaravati.%20On%20the%20other%20side%2C%20they%20say%20that%20I%20had%20insider%20information%20and%20my%20company%20bought%20land%20which%20is%2090%20kilometres%20away%20or%20X%20kilometres%20away%20from%20the%20core%20capital.%20Absolutely%20rubbish%20charges.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWill%20your%20party%20or%20your%20father%20play%20a%20role%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%3F%20He%20was%20a%20part%20of%20that%20opposition%20in%202019.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistorically%2C%20TDP%20has%20been%20an%20anti-Congress%20platform%2C%20because%20we%20believe%20the%20leadership%20of%20Congress%20did%20not%20do%20justice%20to%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%20Mr.%20Naidu%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20United%20Front%20government%2C%20and%20subsequently%20was%20the%20NDA%20convenor%20also%20under%20Vajpayee%20ji%E2%80%99s%20tenure.%20Vajpayee%20ji%20was%20very%20kind%20enough%20to%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20good%20work%20for%20Andhra%20and%20the%20nation%2C%20as%20a%20matter%20of%20fact.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%2C%20our%20stand%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20same%20as%20of%20now.%20We%E2%80%99re%20equidistant%20from%20both%20alliances%20and%20our%20support%20is%20purely%20issue-based.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESo%2C%20will%20TDP%20not%20compromise%20its%20secular%20fundamentals%20in%20case%20it%20supports%20the%20Modi-led%20BJP.%C2%A0%20Continue%20its%20inclusive%20secular%20politics%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETDP%E2%80%99s%20fundamentals%2C%20foundation%20is%20based%20on%20secularism.%20The%20first%20Dalit%20speaker%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%20is%20a%20person%20from%20TDP%2C%20(G.M.C)%20Balayogi%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20right%3F%20The%20first%20woman%20Dalit%20speaker%20in%20the%20assembly%20is%20a%20TDPian.%20(K.)%20Pratibha%20Bharati%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E.%20First%20minority%20person%20that%20went%20to%20Lok%20Sabha%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20was%20(S.M)%20Laljan%20Basha%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20from%20Guntur.%20So%2C%20TDP%20believes%20that%20India%20should%20not%20be%20divided%20along%20religious%20lines.%20We%20are%20a%20union%20of%20states.%20Together%2C%20we%20need%20to%20move%20forward.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20secularism%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20mean%20we%20are%20anti-Hinduism.%20I%20think%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20fine%20line.%20When%20this%20(state)%20government%20got%20formed%2C%20attacks%20on%20temples%20increased.%20And%20in%20Ram%20Tirtham%2C%20which%20is%20a%20very%20historical%20temple%20in%20North%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20idol%20was%20defaced%20and%20Mr.%20Naidu%20went%20there.%20And%20people%20questioned%20me%20and%20I%20asked%20a%20straight%20question%20to%20everyone%20that%20if%20this%20had%20happened%20to%20a%20mosque%2C%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20any%20political%20party%20respond%3F%20The%20same%20thing%20happened%20to%20a%20church%20and%20we%20responded.%20TDP%20is%20a%20secular%20party.%20We%20stand%20by%20Hindus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHow%20do%20you%20weigh%20your%20chances%20in%20these%20elections%3F%20Both%20in%20parliament%20and%20assembly%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20victory%20is%20a%20virtual%20certainty.%20We%20will%20sweep%20all%20regions%2C%20just%20wait%20and%20watch.%20I%20sensed%20anti-incumbency%20against%20Jagan%E2%80%99s%20government%20as%20early%20as%20October%202021.%20That%20is%20when%2C%20in%20my%20own%20constituency%2C%20I%20started%20doing%20a%20door-to-door%20programme%20and%20I%20reported%20back%20to%20Mr.%20Naidu%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20severe%20anti-incumbency%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20when%20we%20did%20this%20programme%20on%20price%20rise%20and%20so%20on%20and%20so%20forth.%20And%20then%20we%20did%20a%20programme%20on%20the%2C%20you%20know%2C%20what%20is%20the%20sorry%20state%20of%20this%20Andhra%20Pradesh%3F%20And%20now%20we%20are%20doing%20a%20programme%20on%20welfare.%20We%E2%80%99re%20going%20to%20do%20a%20programme%20on%20hope.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESo%20you%E2%80%99ve%20been%20active%20all%20these%20five%20years%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWell%2C%20you%20should%20ask%20the%20public.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ESince%20January%2C%20I%20know%20that%20you%E2%80%99ve%20been%20doing%20this%20padayatra.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20have%2022%20cases%20against%20me.%20I%20have%20an%20attempt%20to%20murder%20case%20against%20me%2C%20I%20have%20an%20SC-ST%20atrocity%20case%20against%20me.%20If%20I%20was%20an%20inactive%20politician%20or%20a%20part-time%20politician%2C%20do%20you%20think%20so%20many%20cases%20would%20be%20there%3F%20And%20by%20the%20way%2C%20quite%20a%20few%20people%20sitting%20here%20have%20cases%20against%20them%20also.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20Andhra%20feature.%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENo%2C%20no%2C%20that%20is%20a%20very%20psycho%20Jagan%20feature.%20When%20Mr.%20Naidu%20was%20in%20power%2C%20he%20did%20not%20harass%20Jagan.%20In%20fact%2C%20Jagan%20was%20postponing%20his%20cases.%20You%20know%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20led%20to%20believe%20Raghuram%20Krishnam%20Raju%20filed%20a%20petition%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20He%E2%80%99s%20YSRCP%E2%80%99s%20own%20MP%3B%20he%20claims%20Jagan%20has%20asked%20for%20adjournment%20in%20his%20cases%204%2C000%20times.%20And%20Mr.%20Naidu%2C%20when%20he%20was%20in%20the%20government%2C%20never%20fast-tracked%20his%20cases.%20Mr.%20Naidu%20never%20practised%20vendetta%20politics%20either%20on%20Jagan%20or%20even%20his%20father%2C%20YSR.%20He%20ever%20did.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20fact%2C%20when%20YSR%20had%20a%20life%20threat%2C%20you%20know%2C%20from%20some%20elements%2C%20it%20was%20Mr.%20Naidu%20who%20gave%20him%20security.%20This%20was%20pre-2004.%20That%20is%20what%20Mr%20Naidu%20stands%20for.%20In%20the%20five%20years%20of%20our%20administration%2C%20it%20was%20all%20about%20development%20and%20welfare.%20Otherwise%20why%20would%20so%20many%20companies%20come%20to%20Andhra%3F%20Why%20would%20Kia%20come%2C%20Foxconn%20come%2C%20TCL%20come%2C%20and%20then%20HCL%2C%20Zoho%2C%20Asian%20Paints%2C%20Berger%20Paints%2C%20Apollo%20Tyres%2C%20Hero%20Motors%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20vision%20is%20also%20the%20same.%20Since%20January%2027%2C%20last%20year%2C%20I%20haven%E2%80%99t%20taken%20a%20break%20even%20on%20Saturdays%20and%20Sundays.%20The%20only%20breaks%20in%20this%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eyatra%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20were%20during%20festivals%20because%20our%20leaders%20asked%20me%20to%20do%20so.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20a%20break%20except%20when%20Mr.%20Naidu%20was%20in%20judicial%20remand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EOrganisationally%2C%20are%20you%20appearing%20to%20be%20deep%20rooted%20now%3F%20You%20have%20been%20credited%20with%20increasing%20party%20membership%20by%20quite%20a%20few%20times%20through%20your%20digital%20outreach%20too.%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETDP%20has%20always%20been%20an%20organisationally%20strong%20party%2C%20but%20TDP%20is%20also%20like%20an%20elephant.%20If%20it%20sits%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stand.%20If%20it%20stands%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20run.%20Once%20it%20runs%2C%20anyone%20who%20comes%20opposite%20to%20it%2C%20it%20will%20just%20stomp%20him%20and%20go%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20kind%20of%20momentum%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EWhat%20are%20your%20challenges%20ahead%20of%20elections%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20think%20the%20biggest%20challenge%20we%20will%20face%20is%20misuse%20of%20official%20missionary.%20But%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20reach%20every%20household%20and%20we%20are%20giving%20them%20a%20bond%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20we%20are%20going%20to%20do%20once%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20comes%20back%20to%20power.%20So%20we%20have%20a%20very%20strong%20grassroots%20organisation%2C%20in%20that%20sense.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704349816000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F04110744%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-01-03-at-6.45.06-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-telugu-desam-party-nara-lokesh-jaganmohan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Andhra%20Pradesh%20is%20witnessing%20a%20rebirthed%20Nara%20Lokesh.%20The%20image%20of%20the%20shy%20son%20of%20N.%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20acknowledged%20more%20as%20a%20dynast%20than%20anything%20else%2C%20has%20given%20way%20to%20a%20diligent%20and%20an%20energetic%20leader%20in%20the%20making.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-telugu-desam-party-nara-lokesh-jaganmohan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Nevada%20judge%20attacked%20by%20defendant%20during%20sentencing%20in%20Vegas%20courtroom%20scene%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704349638000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106535971%2Cimgsize-820010.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwatch-nevada-judge-attacked-by-defendant-during-sentencing-in-vegas-courtroom-scene%2Farticleshow%2F106535897.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106535897.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwatch-nevada-judge-attacked-by-defendant-during-sentencing-in-vegas-courtroom-scene%2Farticleshow%2F106535897.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwatch-nevada-judge-attacked-by-defendant-during-sentencing-in-vegas-courtroom-scene%2Famp_articleshow%2F106535897.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwatch-nevada-judge-attacked-by-defendant-during-sentencing-in-vegas-courtroom-scene%2Famp_articleshow%2F106535897.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Almost%20150%20Earthquakes%20Struck%20Japan%20in%20Less%20Than%20a%20Day%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20big%20earthquake%20rattled%20Japan's%20northwestern%20coast%20on%20New%20Year's%20day%2C%20killing%20dozens%20and%20rekindling%20fears%20of%20the%20tsunami%20that%20ravaged%20the%20nation's%20northern%20region%20in%202011.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20about%20150%20to%20strike%20the%20region%20over%20the%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan%20is%20located%20in%20one%20of%20the%20most%20active%20seismic%20regions%20in%20the%20world%2C%20with%20the%20whole%20country%20at%20risk%20of%20being%20affected%20by%20quakes.%20Here's%20a%20look%20at%20the%20quake%20and%20its%20effects.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20magnitude%207.6%20earthquake%20struck%20off%20the%20Noto%20Peninsula%20on%20Japan's%20northwest%20coast%20on%20Jan.%201%20just%20after%204%20p.m.%20locally%2C%20killing%20at%20least%2048%20people%20and%20injuring%20many%20more%2C%20according%20to%20local%20officials.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECollapsed%20houses%20following%20an%20earthquake%20in%20Nanao%2C%20Ishikawa%20Prefecture%2C%20Japan%2C%20on%20January%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20quake%20triggered%20a%20tsunami%20warning%20for%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20country's%20Sea%20of%20Japan%20coastline%20on%20Jan.%201%2C%20gripping%20the%20nation%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20New%20Year%2C%20when%20many%20were%20celebrating%20with%20friends%20and%20family.%20The%20Japan%20Meteorological%20Agency%20issued%20a%20warning%20for%20a%20wave%20of%20up%20five%20meters%20(16%20feet)%20on%20January%201%2C%20but%20it%20lifted%20all%20tsunami%20alerts%20on%20Tuesday%20at%2010%20a.m.%20after%20recording%20a%20wave%20of%20at%20least%201.2%20meters%20in%20height.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20quakes%20in%20Japan%20since%202018%20and%20resulted%20in%20damage%20to%20at%20least%20200%20structures%2C%20left%20thousands%20without%20power%20and%20running%20water%2C%20and%20caused%20stoppages%20to%20rail%20and%20road%20traffic%20around%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20more%20quakes%20expected%20imminently%3F%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPast%20instances%20show%20there%20is%20a%20risk%20of%20up%20to%2020%25%20that%20another%20quake%20of%20the%20same%20size%20could%20take%20place%2C%20the%20Japan%20Meteorological%20Agency%20said%20in%20a%20press%20briefing.%20Residents%20in%20the%20area%20continue%20to%20be%20hit%20by%20frequent%20aftershocks%2C%20which%20are%20putting%20structures%20in%20the%20region%20at%20even%20greater%20risk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20in%20areas%20worst%20affected%20should%20be%20on%20alert%20over%20the%20next%20week%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20large%20earthquakes%20and%20potentially%20tsunami%2C%20according%20to%20JMA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20worst%20case%20scenario%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20worst%20case%20scenario%20is%20that%20an%20additional%20large%20earthquake%20could%20hit%20the%20northwest%20and%20trigger%20a%20tsunami%20of%20the%20scale%20that%20authorities%20initially%20warned%20about%20on%20Jan.%201.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20did%20the%20quakes%20occur%20in%20a%20cluster%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20number%20of%20active%20faults%20off%20the%20Noto%20Peninsula%2C%20with%20the%20compression%20pushing%20underground%20plates%20together%20and%20forcing%20one%20above%20the%20other%2C%20according%20to%20Japan's%20Headquarters%20for%20Earthquake%20Research%20Promotion.%20This%20is%20known%20as%20a%20reverse-type%20fault%20mechanism.%20Earthquakes%20have%20been%20increasing%20in%20the%20area%20since%202018%2C%20with%20seismic%20activity%20becoming%20higher%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20more%20than%2014%2C000%20small%20earthquakes%20occurring%20off%20the%20Noto%20peninsula%20in%20seismic%20swarm%20from%20November%202020%20to%20February%202023%20with%20a%20magnitude%20of%201%20or%20more%2C%20according%20to%20a%20paper%20by%20experts%20at%20Japanese%20universities.%20A%206.5%20magnitude%20earthquake%20in%20the%20Noto%20area%20killed%20at%20least%20one%20person%20in%20May%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20the%20changes%20in%20crustal%20deformation%20zones%20in%20the%20region%2C%20it's%20possible%20that%20fluid%20movements%20were%20involved%20in%20earlier%20quakes%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20released%20by%20the%20government's%20earthquake%20research%20council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20earthquake%20in%20the%20Noto%20peninsula%20over%20the%20last%20century%20was%20the%20Noto-Hanto%20earthquake%20that%20occurred%20on%20March%2025%2C%202007%20with%20a%20magnitude%20of%206.9.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20dangerous%20can%20quakes%20be%20in%20Japan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Japan%2C%20thousands%20of%20people%20have%20died%20due%20to%20major%20earthquakes%20in%20recent%20decades%2C%20with%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20northern%20region%20needing%20to%20be%20rebuilt%20after%20what%20is%20locally%20called%20the%20Great%20East%20Japan%20Earthquake%20of%202011.%20That%20earthquake%20and%20subsequent%20tsunami%20resulted%20in%20about%2020%2C000%20deaths%20with%20about%202%2C500%20going%20missing%2C%20according%20to%20government%20statistics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThousands%20of%20buildings%20were%20damaged%2C%20with%20more%20than%20120%2C000%20totally%20collapsing%20in%202011.%20The%20disaster%20also%20resulted%20in%20Japan's%20worst%20nuclear%20disaster%20at%20Tokyo%20Electric's%20Fukushima%20plant%2C%20requiring%20the%20government%20to%20bail%20out%20the%20utility.%20The%20government%20raised%20taxes%20to%20rebuild%20its%20northern%20regions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201995%2C%20more%20than%206%2C000%20people%20died%20in%20the%20Kobe%20earthquake%2C%20while%20in%20more%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20Kumamoto%20earthquake%20in%202016%20killed%20over%20200%20people.%20The%20death%20count%20from%20an%20earthquake%20that%20struck%20Tokyo%20in%201923%20is%20believed%20to%20have%20exceeded%20100%2C000%2C%20according%20to%20official%20statistics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20Japan%20have%20a%20warning%20system%20in%20place%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan's%20meteorological%20agency%20has%20an%20earthquake%20early%20warning%20(EEW)%20system%20that%20has%20been%20in%20place%20since%202007.%20Authorities%20have%20improved%20measurement%20techniques%20since%20the%20events%20of%202011%20and%202016%20to%20better%20judge%20the%20size%20of%20multiple%20earthquakes%20occurring%20at%20the%20same%20time.%20But%20the%20EEW%20system%20has%20still%20sent%20false%20alarms%2C%20including%20in%202018%20and%202020%2C%20causing%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapanese%20residents%20with%20smartphones%20receive%20loud%20alerts%20on%20their%20phones%20in%20the%20case%20of%20a%20sizable%20earthquake%2C%20warning%20them%20to%20take%20safety%20precautions.%20In%20Japan%2C%20residents%20are%20well%20used%20to%20earthquakes%20and%20one%20of%20the%20first%20things%20they%20do%20when%20feeling%20a%20tremor%20is%20to%20turn%20on%20the%20national%20broadcaster%20NHK%20which%20carries%20extensive%20coverage%2C%20while%20other%20TV%20stations%20also%20flash%20quake%20alerts%20across%20their%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20also%20increasingly%20rely%20on%20the%20Internet%20for%20quick%20information%2C%20even%20though%20it%20contains%20inaccurate%20or%20misleading%20information.%20Prime%20Minister%20Fumio%20Kishida%20urged%20strict%20caution%20against%20the%20spread%20of%20misinformation%20that%20could%20amplify%20confusion%20in%20the%20field.%20Also%2C%20despite%20the%20growing%20importance%20of%20mobile%20services%2C%20major%20telecommunications%20carriers%20have%20often%20reported%20connection%20failures%20after%20earthquakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704349440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fburlhttg_japan-quakes_120x90_04_January_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhy-almost-150-earthquakes-struck-japan-in-less-than-a-day-4797653%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20big%20earthquake%20rattled%20Japan's%20northwestern%20coast%20on%20New%20Year's%20day%2C%20killing%20dozens%20and%20rekindling%20fears%20of%20the%20tsunami%20that%20ravaged%20the%20nation's%20northern%20region%20in%202011.%20It%20was%20one%20of%20about%20150%20to%20strike%20the%20region%20o