Their%20Appearance%3A%20SC%20to%20All%20Courts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20(January%203)%20laid%20down%20rules%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20courts%20while%20summoning%20government%20officials.%20In%20the%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedures%2C%20the%20apex%20court%20said%20that%20judges%20should%20avoid%20humiliating%20such%20officials%20or%20making%20unnecessary%20comments%20on%20their%20attire%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fsupreme-court-lays-down-rules-summoning-government-officials-asks-courts-not-humiliate%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20and%20Justices%20J.B.%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Mishra%20also%20said%20that%20courts%20should%20avoid%20arbitrarily%20summoning%20officials%2C%20and%20officials%20should%20not%20be%20summoned%20if%20the%20issue%20can%20be%20sorted%20out%20through%20an%20affidavit%20instead%20of%20physical%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20also%20should%20not%20be%20summoned%20only%20because%20their%20view%20may%20be%20different%20from%20that%20of%20the%20court.%20However%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%2C%20the%20physical%20presence%20of%20government%20officials%20may%20be%20required%20in%20cases%20where%20there%20has%20been%20a%20suppression%20of%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourts%20must%20also%20not%20comment%20of%20government%20officials%E2%80%99%20attire%20%E2%80%9Cunless%20there%20is%20violation%20of%20dress%20code%20of%20their%20own%20office%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20was%20hearing%20a%20petition%20filed%20by%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20government%20against%20orders%20passed%20by%20Allahabad%20high%20court%20last%20year%20to%20summon%20two%20senior%20government%20officers.%20The%20court%20set%20aside%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20orders%2C%20including%20one%20which%20had%20directed%20the%20arrest%20of%20two%20IAS%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCompelling%20the%20State%20Government%20to%20mandatorily%20notify%20the%20Rules%20by%20the%20next%20date%20of%20hearing%2C%20in%20the%20First%20Impugned%20Order%2C%20virtually%20amounted%20to%20the%20High%20Court%20issuing%20a%20writ%20of%20mandamus%20to%20notify%20the%20Rules%20proposed%20by%20the%20Chief%20Justice.%20Such%20directions%20by%20the%20High%20Court%20are%20impermissible%20and%20contrary%20to%20the%20separation%20of%20powers%20envisaged%20by%20the%20Constitution.%20The%20High%20Court%20cannot%20direct%20the%20State%20Government%20to%20enact%20rules%20on%20a%20particular%20subject%2C%20by%20a%20writ%20of%20mandamus%20or%20otherwise%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20apex%20court%20said%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704347628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdont-summon-govt-officials-arbitrarily-or-comment-on-their-appearance-sc-to-all-courts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22However%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%2C%20the%20physical%20presence%20of%20government%20officials%20may%20be%20required%20in%20cases%20where%20there%20has%20been%20a%20suppression%20of%20evidence.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fdont-summon-govt-officials-arbitrarily-or-comment-on-their-appearance-sc-to-all-courts%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22State-owned%20PFC%20commits%20Rs%2025%2C000%20cr%20for%20power%20sector%20projects%20in%20Gujarat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22publishe