ct%20the%20pitch%20to%20assist%20that%20much.%20Also%2C%20bowling%20is%20all%20about%20partnerships.%20There%20was%20consistent%20pressure%20from%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Jasprit%20Bumrah%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1724-jasprit-bumrah-playerprofile%5C%22%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20other%20end.%20He%20didn't%20get%20many%20wickets%20but%20he%20created%20a%20lot%20of%20pressure%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Siraj%20in%20the%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESiraj%20also%20revealed%20his%20plan%20as%20he%20stuck%20to%20keeping%20the%20same%20line%20and%20length%20instead%20of%20experimentation%20in%20a%20bid%20to%20reap%20the%20sort%20of%20rewards%20he%20did%20on%20Day%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20these%20wickets%2C%20where%20ball%20is%20doing%20so%20much%2C%20often%20bowlers%20tend%20to%20think%2C%20'let%20me%20try%20and%20bowl%20an%20outswinger%20darting%20from%20leg%20to%20off%20or%20get%20one%20to%20bend%20back%20from%20angle%20but%20one%20should%20just%20stick%20to%20one%20line.%20If%20you%20hit%20areas%2C%20wickets%20will%20come%20automatically.%20If%20you%20try%20many%20things%2C%20you%20can%20get%20confused%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Siraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20elected%20to%20bat%20first%20and%20was%20bundled%20out%20for%20just%2055%20in%2023.2%20overs%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kyle%20Verreynne%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F112791-kyle-verreynne-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKyle%20Verreynne%3C%2Fa%3E%20(15)%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22David%20Bedingham%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F120133-david-bedingham-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDavid%20Bedingham%3C%2Fa%3E%20(12)%20being%20the%20sole%20players%20to%20touch%20double%20digits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Siraj's%20fiery%20spell%20of%206%2F15%20destroyed%20Proteas'%20top%20and%20middle%20order%2C%20while%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20(2%2F25)%20and%20%3Ca%20