20after%20January%201%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20provide%20insight%20into%20the%20connections%20between%20Epstein%20and%20these%20prominent%20figures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20comes%20several%20years%20after%20Virginia%20Giuffre%2C%20a%20victim%2C%20filed%20a%20case%20against%20British%20socialite%2C%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%2C%20accusing%20her%20of%20being%20involved%20in%20the%20alleged%20sex%20trafficking%20activities%20of%20Jeffrey%20Epstein.%20Giuffre%20accused%20Maxwell%20of%20defaming%20her%20by%20publicly%20denying%20Giuffre's%20claims%20of%20sexual%20trafficking%20and%20abuse%20that%20she%20suffered%20as%20a%20minor%20during%201999-2002.%20Despite%20facing%20legal%20scrutiny%20for%20these%20accusations%2C%20Epstein's%20prosecution%20abruptly%20came%20to%20a%20halt%20when%20he%20took%20his%20own%20life%20by%20hanging%20in%20a%20New%20York%20prison%20in%20August%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBill%20Clinton's%20Connection%20To%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBill%20Clinton%2C%20referred%20to%20as%20%26quot%3BDoe%2036%26quot%3B%20in%20court%20documents%2C%20is%20mentioned%2050%20times%20in%20sealed%20records.%20Although%20Virginia%20Giuffre%20didn't%20accuse%20Clinton%2C%20she%20claimed%20to%20have%20seen%20him%20with%20two%20young%20women%20on%20Epstein's%20island%2C%20which%20he%20denies%20ever%20visiting.%20Despite%20Clinton's%20denial%2C%20flight%20records%20show%20he%20used%20Epstein's%20plane%20for%20international%20trips%20after%20his%20presidency%2C%20going%20to%20places%20like%20Paris%2C%20Bangkok%2C%20and%20Brunei.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20the%20records%2C%20another%20victim%2C%20Johanna%20Sjoberg%20testified%20that%20Epstein%20once%20told%20her%20that%20Bill%20Clinton%20%26quot%3Blikes%20them%20young%2C%26quot%3B%20referring%20to%20girls.%20Bill%20Clinton%20also%20had%20an%20affair%20with%20a%2022-year-old%20White%20House%20intern%20during%20his%20time%20as%20the%20U.S.%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EStephen%20Hawking's%20Connection%20To%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%202015%2C%20shortly%20after%20Virginia%20Giuffre%20filed%20a%20civil%20claim%20in%20the%20U.S.%2C%20an%20email%20from%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20to%20the%20disgraced%20British%20socialite%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20revealed%20that%20Epstein%20had%20asked%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bissue%20a%20reward%26quot%3B%20to%20any%20of%20Giuffre's%20friends%20as%20a%20means%20to%20counter%20her%20claims%20of%20Professor%20Stephen%20Hawking%20participating%20in%20an%20underage%20orgy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20issue%20a%20reward%20to%20any%20of%20Virginia's%20friends%2C%20acquaints%2C%20family%20that%20come%20forward%20and%20help%20prove%20her%20allegations%20are%20false.%20The%20strongest%20is%20the%20Clinton%20dinner%2C%20and%20the%20new%20version%20in%20the%20Virgin%20Islands%20that%20Stephen%20Hawking%20participated%20in%20an%20underage%20orgy%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20email%20read%2C%20as%20per%20Irish%20News.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrince%20Andrew's%20Connection%20To%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EVirginia%20Giuffre%20mentioned%20a%20disturbing%20incident%20in%20March%202001%20when%20she%20claimed%20to%20be%20trafficked%20to%20Prince%20Andrew%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bwicked%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Breally%20scary%20time.%26quot%3B%20She%20claimed%20that%20after%20a%20nightclub%20visit%2C%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20instructed%20her%20to%20%26quot%3Bdo%20for%20Andrew%20what%20I%20do%20for%20Jeffrey.%26quot%3B%20Prince%20Andrew%20said%20he%20never%20met%20Virginia%20Giuffre%20and%20denied%20her%20claims.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20files%20also%20mention%20Johanna%20Sjoberg%2C%C2%A0%20who%20has%20claimed%20that%20Prince%20Andrew%20groped%20her%20breast%20while%20they%20were%20seated%20on%20a%20couch%20inside%20Jeffrey%20Epstein's%20Manhattan%20apartment%20in%202001.%20In%20one%20reported%20deposition%2C%20Sjoberg%20claimed%20Prince%20Andrew%20placed%20his%20hand%20on%20her%20breast%20for%20a%20photo%2C%20reports%20BBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELarry%20Page's%20Connection%20To%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20US%20Virgin%20Islands%20government%20attempted%20to%20serve%20a%20subpoena%20on%20Google%20co-founder%20Larry%20Page%20to%20obtain%20documents%20for%20its%20civil%20lawsuit%20against%20JPMorgan%20Chase.%20The%20lawsuit%20is%20connected%20to%20allegations%20of%20sex%20trafficking%20by%20the%20bank's%20longtime%20customer%2C%20Jeffrey%20Epstein.%20%E2%80%9CLarry%20Page%20%E2%80%94the%20co-founder%20and%20co-owner%20of%20Alphabet%20Inc.%20(Google%20LLC's%20parent%20company)%E2%80%94is%20a%20high-net-worth%20individual%20who%20Epstein%20may%20have%20referred%20or%20attempted%20to%20refer%20to%20JPMorgan%E2%80%9D%20as%20a%20customer%2C%20lawyers%20said%20in%20their%20court%20filing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGlenn%20Dubin's%20Connection%20To%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20her%20lawsuit%2C%20Virginia%20Giuffre%20stated%20that%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%20had%20asked%20her%20to%20give%20Billionaire%20hedge%20fund%20manager%20Glenn%20Dubin%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmassage%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%20She%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20when%20they%20say%20massage%2C%20that%20means%20erotic%2C%20okay%3F%20That's%20their%20term%20for%20it.%20I%20think%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20other%20witnesses%20who%20can%20attest%20to%20what%20massage%20actually%20means.%20And%20I'm%20telling%20you%20that%20Ghislaine%20told%20me%20to%20go%20to%20Glenn%20Dubin%20and%20give%20him%20a%20massage%2C%20which%20means%20sex%2C%E2%80%9D%20as%20per%20court%20documents%2C%20released%20by%20Forbes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20addition%20to%20the%20mentioned%20figures%2C%20other%20personalities%20such%20as%20Nobel%20laureate%20Lawrence%20Krauss%2C%20Michael%20Jackson%2C%20magician%20David%20Copperfield%2C%20comedian%20Chris%20Tucker%2C%20actor%20Kevin%20Spacey%2C%20Victoria's%20Secret%20magnate%20Les%20Wexner%20and%20model%20Naomi%20Campbell%20were%20reported%20to%20have%20visited%20Jeffrey%20Epstein's%20island.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20court%20documents%20from%20a%20civil%20suit%20unsealed%20in%202019%2C%20Virginia%20Giuffre%20named%20several%20individuals%20whom%20she%20claims%20Epstein%20and%20Maxwell%20instructed%20her%20to%20have%20sex%20with%2C%20including%20attorney%20Alan%20Dershowitz%2C%20politician%20Bill%20Richardson%2C%20the%20late%20MIT%20scientist%20Marvin%20Minsky%2C%20lawyer%20George%20J.%20Mitchell%2C%20and%20MC2%20modelling%20agent%20Jean-Luc%20Brunel.%C2%A0%20Many%20of%20the%20accused%20have%20denied%20Giuffre's%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704345720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-04%2Fsjitk4a4_stephen-hawking-reuters-650_625x300_23_April_20.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjeffrey-epstein-probe-bill-clinton-donald-trump-stephen-hawking-who-are-named-in-epstein-files-4797329%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20a%20significant%20legal%20development%2C%20hundreds%20of%20sealed%20court%20filings%20linked%20to%20the%20notorious%20late%20sex%20offender%20Jeffrey%20Epstein%20are%20slated%20to%20be%20revealed%20this%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjeffrey-epstein-probe-bill-clinton-donald-trump-stephen-hawking-who-are-named-in-epstein-files-4797329%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjeffrey-epstein-probe-bill-clinton-donald-trump-stephen-hawking-who-are-named-in-epstein-files-4797329%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fww