y%20morning%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20dispatch%20of%20seven%20fire%20tenders%20by%20Delhi%20Fire%20Services.%20The%20fire%2C%20which%20damaged%20furniture%2C%20a%20refrigerator%2C%20and%20office%20records%20on%20the%20second%20floor%20of%20the%20director's%20building%2C%20was%20successfully%20extinguished.%20Fortunately%2C%20there%20have%20been%20no%20reported%20casualties%20or%20injuries%20as%20a%20result%20of%20the%20incident.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Ffire-breaks-out-at-teaching-block-of-aiims-delhi-doused%2Farticleshow%2F106533472.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Mathematicians%20Ensure%20Lottery%20Victory%20With%20Only%2027%20Ticket%20Purchase%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ELast%20July%2C%20two%20British%20mathematicians%20found%20a%20way%20to%20win%20the%20UK%20national%20lottery%20by%20buying%20just%2027%20tickets%20out%20of%20over%2045%20million%20possibilities.%20They%20were%20surprised%20to%20see%20their%20discovery%20become%20famous%20worldwide%2C%20and%20many%20people%20tried%20playing%20with%20the%20suggested%2027%20tickets%2C%20getting%20different%20results.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reality%20is%20that%20the%20two%20mathematicians%2C%20David%20Stewart%20and%20David%20Cushing%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Manchester%2C%20cannot%20guarantee%20you%20a%20jackpot%20win.%20However%2C%20in%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpure.manchester.ac.uk%2Fws%2Fportalfiles%2Fportal%2F272368587%2F2307.12430v1.pdf%5C%22%3Epaper%20from%20July%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20claimed%20to%20have%20determined%20the%20minimum%20number%20of%20tickets%20required%20to%20guarantee%20some%20kind%20of%20win%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20just%20a%20free%20play.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20UK%20National%20Lottery%2C%20players%20purchase%20tickets%20comprising%20their%20choices%20of%20six%20different%20numbers%20between%201%20and%2059.%20During%20the%20draw%2C%20six%20balls%20are%20randomly%20selected%20without%20replacement%20from%20a%20set%20numbered%20from%201%20to%2059%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20author%20of%20the%20research%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.researchgate.net%2Fpublication%2F372584308_You_need_27_tickets_to_guarantee_a_win_on_the_UK_National_Lottery%5C%22%3Esaid.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20prize%20is%20awarded%20to%20any%20player%20who%20matches%20at%20least%20two%20of%20the%20six%20drawn%20numbers.%20We%20identify%2027%20tickets%20that%20guarantee%20a%20prize%2C%20regardless%20of%20which%20of%20the%2045%2C057%2C474%20possible%20draws%20occurs.%20Moreover%2C%20we%20determine%20that%2027%20is%20the%20optimal%20number%20of%20tickets%20required%2C%20as%20achieving%20the%20same%20guarantee%20with%2026%20tickets%20is%20not%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20mathematicians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20identify%20the%20combinations%2C%20the%20researchers%20employed%20a%20mathematical%20approach%20known%20as%20finite%20geometry.%20This%20method%20entails%20arranging%20the%20numbers%20one%20to%2059%20in%20pairs%20or%20triplets%20on%20various%20geometric%20shapes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20each%20set%20of%20numbers%20is%20linked%20with%20lines%2C%20creating%20a%20sequence%20of%20six%20numbers%2C%20which%20corresponds%20to%20one%20lottery%20ticket.%20According%20to%20their%20findings%2C%20it%20requires%2027%20of%20these%20tickets%20to%20encompass%20all%2059%20numbers%20and%20ensure%20that%20at%20least%20one%20pair%20will%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704345120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Ftairicd4_lottery-generic_625x300_05_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fscience%2Fuk-mathematicians-claim-a-guaranteed-lottery-win-using-just-27-purchased-tickets-4797192%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Dr%20David%20Stewart%20and%20Dr%20David%20Cushing%20exam