C%20is%2067%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fed-to-drop-case-against-two-dalit-farmers-after-outrage-101704307852951.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20TNM%20describes%20them%20as%20%E2%80%9Cin%20their%2070s.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20own%206.5%20acres%20of%20land%20in%20the%20village%20and%20subsist%20on%20Rs%201%2C000%20of%20monthly%20pension.%20The%20two%20have%20reportedly%20accused%20a%20local%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20leader%20of%20trying%20to%20illegally%20grab%20their%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20envelope%20carrying%20the%20ED%20summons%20said%20the%20farmers%20were%20%E2%80%98Hindu%20Pallars%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigating%20officer%20is%20one%20Ritesh%20Kumar%20who%20asked%20the%20two%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20agency%20on%20July%205%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20summons%20surfaced%20on%20social%20media%20to%20widespread%20outrage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ETimes%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20quoted%20unnamed%20officials%20to%20say%20that%20the%20case%20was%20closed%2C%20as%20the%20predicate%20offence%20based%20on%20which%20the%20probe%20began%20was%20already%20over.%20The%20officials%20told%20the%20paper%20that%20the%20agency%20had%20no%20intentions%20of%20harassing%20the%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20said%20that%20the%20case%20was%20%E2%80%9Cbased%20on%20a%20letter%20forwarded%20by%20Tamil%20Nadu%20forest%20department%20on%20July%2012%2C%202021%E2%80%B3%20and%20was%20related%20to%20the%20killing%20of%20two%20wild%20buffaloes%20under%20section%2051%20and%209%20of%20Wildlife%20Protection%20Act%2C%201972.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20immediately%20clear%20why%20the%20ED%20was%20tackling%20wildlife%20cases%2C%20even%20though%20the%20official%20cites%20a%20Financial%20Action%20Task%20Force%20mandate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20farmers%E2%80%99%20lawyer%20had