e-begins-of-potentially-explosive-jeffrey-epstein-court-documents-iding-dozens%2F%5C%22%3Ereportedly%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20referred%20to%20more%20than%2050%20times%20in%20the%20redacted%20documents%20as%20%26quot%3BJohn%20Doe%2036.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClinton's%20spokesperson%20clarified%20that%20it%20has%20been%20nearly%20two%20decades%20since%20Clinton%20last%20had%20contact%20with%20Epstein%2C%20emphasising%20that%20Clinton%20has%20not%20faced%20any%20accusations%20of%20criminal%20activity%20in%20relation%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECourt%20documents%20unveiled%20an%20email%20from%20Epstein%20to%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%2C%20his%20associate%2C%20proposing%20a%20reward%20to%20disprove%20allegations%20made%20by%20Virginia%20Giuffre.%20The%20email%20outlines%20a%20plan%20to%20counter%20Giuffre's%20claims%2C%20including%20the%20sensational%20allegation%20that%20physicist%20Stephen%20Hawking%20participated%20in%20an%20underage%20orgy.%20However%2C%20Epstein's%20emails%20to%20Maxwell%20refute%20that%20claim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESjoberg's%20deposition%20also%20included%20a%20mention%20of%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20with%20Epstein%20allegedly%20suggesting%20they%20contact%20Trump%20during%20a%20flight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relationship%20between%20Maxwell%20and%20Epstein%20evolved%20from%20a%20romantic%20connection%20in%20the%20early%201990s%20to%20a%20disturbing%20partnership%20in%20sex%20crimes%20spanning%20nearly%20three%20decades.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEpstein%2C%20a%20well-connected%20financier%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20abroad%2C%20faced%20accusations%20of%20sexually%20assaulting%20young%20girls.%20However%2C%20his%20suicide%20by%20hanging%20in%20a%20New%20York%20prison%20in%20August%202019%20abruptly%20halted%20the%20legal%20proceedings%20against%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704343020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2F6g7no6d8_epstein-bill-clinton-_625x300_04_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID