%20day%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20between%20India%20and%20South%20Africa%20with%20several%20world%20records%20being%20broken.%20After%20South%20Africa%20chose%20to%20bat%20first%2C%20the%20hosts%20lost%2010%20wickets%20in%20the%20first%20session%20as%20they%20were%20all%20out%20for%2055.%20It's%20the%20lowest%20all-out%20score%20by%20a%20team%20against%20India%20in%20Tests.%20Then%20India%20got%20out%20for%20153%2C%20losing%20their%20last%20six%20wickets%20for%200%20-%20which%20is%20a%20world%20record.%20At%20stumps%2C%20India%20had%20gained%20control%20with%20South%20Africa%20reeling%20at%2062%2F3%20in%20their%20second%20innings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incidents%20of%20the%20day%20surprised%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20stars%20too%20who%20were%20commentating%20on%20the%20match.%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sanjay%20Manjrekar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F41124-sanjay-vijay-manjrekar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESanjay%20Manjrekar%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20predicted%20four%20wickets%20in%20the%20first%20session%20while%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Piyush%20Chawla%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F743-piyush-chawla-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPiyush%20Chawla%3C%2Fa%3E%20predicted%20three%20wickets.%20Both%20were%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20be%20sacked%20for%20our%20poor%20prediction.%20I%20said%204%2C%20he%20said%203%2C%26quot%3B%20Manjrekar%20said%20on%20Star%20Sports.%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Mohammed%20Siraj%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107503-mohammed-siraj-playerprofile%5C%22%3EMohammed%20Siraj%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20not%20trying%20to%20swing%20the%20ball.%20Just%20watch%20all%20the%20deliveries%2C%20the%20balls%20that%20got%20him%20wickets.%20No%20one%20is%20floating%20the%20ball%20up%20and%20trying%20to%20get%20a%20swing.%20This%20is%20the%20South%20African%20way%20of%20getting%20wickets%20in%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20something%20about%20an%20action%20that%20is%20repeatable.%20Siraj%20is%20a%20type%20of%20bowler%2C%20if%20he%20has%203%20wickets%20in%205%20overs%2C%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20give%20him%20a%20break.%20He%20would%20want%20to%20go%20on%20and%20on.%20He%20is%20somebody%20who%20would%20bowl%2012%20overs%20in%20a%20session%2C%26quot%3B%20Manjrekar%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20match%2C%20Mohammed%20Siraj%20got%20six%20wickets%20in%20a%20breathtakingly%20menacing%20morning%20spell%20but%20to%20his%20horror%20found%20India%20losing%20six%20wickets%20in%20a%20space%20of%20eleven%20balls%20in%20the%20final%20session%20before%20regaining%20the%20advantage%20against%20South%20Africa%20on%20a%20rivetting%20day%20one%20of%20the%20second%20Test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Siraj's%20career-best%206%2F15%20decimated%20South%20Africa%20for%20their%20lowest%20post-apartheid%20score%20of%2055%2C%20India%20were%20153%20for%204%20before%20losing%20six%20wickets%20without%20addition%20of%20single%20run%20in%20a%20space%20of%2011%20deliveries%20to%20end%20with%20a%2098-run%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20six%20Indian%20batters%2C%20who%20failed%20to%20open%20their%20accounts%20and%20one%20who%20remained%20not%20out%20also%20didn't%20trouble%20the%20scorer%2C%20making%20it%20a%20statistician's%20nightmare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Lungi%20Ngidi%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64640-lungisani-ngidi-playerprofile%5C%22%3ELungi%20Ngidi%3C%2Fa%3E%20(3%2F30)%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kagiso%20Rabada%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F64042-kagiso-rabada-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKagiso%20Rabada%3C%2Fa%3E%20(3%2F38)%20got%20five%20of%20those%20six%20wickets%20keeping%20the%20lead%20below%20100%20and%20gaining%20the%20necessary%20psychological%20advantage%20as%2023%20wickets%20fell%20on%20the%20opening%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20