E2%80%9CI%20conveyed%20the%20criticality%20of%20the%20situation%20to%20the%20RM%20(Raksha%20Mantri)%2C%20who%20said%20he%20would%20get%20back%20to%20me%2C%20which%20he%20did%2C%20by%20about%202230%20hours%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHe%20said%20that%20he%20had%20spoken%20to%20the%20PM%20and%20that%20it%20was%20purely%20a%20military%20decision.%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EJo%20ucchit%20samjho%20woh%20karo%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(Do%20whatever%20you%20deem%20is%20appropriate).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20handed%20a%20hot%20potato.%20With%20this%20carte%20blanche%2C%20the%20onus%20was%20now%20totally%20on%20me.%20I%20took%20a%20deep%20breath%20and%20sat%20silently%20for%20a%20few%20minutes.%20All%20was%20quiet%20save%20for%20the%20ticking%20of%20the%20wall%20clock.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CXi%20Jinping%20won%E2%80%99t%20forget%20June%2016%2C%202020%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaravane%20also%20writes%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Findian-army-officers-killed-china-galwan-valley%5C%22%3EGalwan%20Valley%20clash%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20June%2016%2C%202020%20when%2020%20Indian%20soldiers%20were%20killed%2C%20referring%20to%20it%20as%20%E2%80%9Cone%20the%20saddest%20days%E2%80%9D%20of%20his%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20excerpts%20published%20by%20PTI%2C%20he%20also%20writes%20that%20the%20Chinese%20president%20Xi%20Jinping%20will%20not%20forget%20the%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJune%2016%20is%20(Chinese%20President)%20Xi%20Jinping%E2%80%99s%20birthday.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20day%20he%20will%20forget%20any%20time%20soon.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20over%20two%20decades%2C%20the%20Chinese%20and%20the%20PLA%20had%20suffered%20fatal%20casualties%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20wrote%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Csavagery%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Chinese%20response%20showed%20that%20they%20had%20suffered%20losses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20men%20who%20were%20in%20Chinese%20hands%20had%20been%20kept%20out%20in%20the%20open%20and%20they%20had%20seen%20several%20bodies%20being%20fished%20out%20of%20the%20river.%20Whenever%20that%20happened%2C%20they%20were%20subjected%20to%20a%20fresh%20round%20of%20beatings%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20sheer%20savagery%20of%20their%20response%20was%20in%20itself%20indicative%20of%20the%20losses%20they%20had%20suffered.%20Initially%2C%20they%20did%20not%20admit%20to%20any%20casualties%20at%20all%3B%20then%20many%20months%20later%2C%20admitted%20to%20four%20or%20five%20killed%2C%20including%20the%20CO%20on%20their%20side.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20mention%20in%20the%20excerpts%20released%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fchina-releases-10-indian-army-soldiers-majors-talks-ladakh-1690509-2020-06-19%5C%22%3Eof%20the%2010%20Indian%20soldiers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20four%20officers%2C%20who%20were%20held%20captive%20for%20three%20days%20before%20being%20released%20by%20the%20Chinese%20army%2C%20as%20per%20some%20reports%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F7ak7tshMJEU%3Fstart%3D21%26feature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22%26quot%3B%E0%A4%85%E0%A4%97%E0%A5%8D%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%B5%E0%A5%80%E0%A4%B0%20%E0%A4%AF%E0%A5%8B%E0%A4%9C%E0%A4%A8%E0%A4%BE%20%E0%A4%A6%E0%A5%87%E0%A4%B6%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%B2%E0%A4%BF%E0%A4%8F%20%E0%A4%96%E0%A4%A4%E0%A4%B0%E0%A5%87%20%E0%A4%95%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%98%E0%A4%82%E0%A4%9F%E0%A5%80%20%E0%A4%B9%E0%A5%88%26quot%3B%20%7C%20Agniveer%20%7C%20Indian%20Army%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAgnipath%20scheme%20%E2%80%98bolt%20out%20of%20the%20blue%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20had%20first%20sounded%20out%20the%20PM%20about%20the%20Tour%20of%20Duty%20scheme%2C%20it%20was%20more%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20a%20short-service%20option%20at%20the%20soldier%20level%2C%20similar%20to%20the%20Short%20Service%20Commission%20scheme%20for%20officers%20that%20was%20already%20in%20vogue%2C%E2%80%9D%20PTI%20quoted%20him%20as%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20as%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20SSC%20officers%20are%20taken%20each%20year%2C%20likewise%20a%20limited%20number%20of%20jawans%20would%20be%20similarly%20enrolled%20and%20released%20after%20the%20completion%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98tour%E2%80%99%20with%20the%20option%20of%20re-enlisting%20for%20another%20tour%2C%20if%20found%20to%20be%20fit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20nothing%20much%20happened%20in%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20months%20with%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20office%20(PMO)%20was%20considering%20this%20proposal%2C%20but%20with%20a%20much%20wider%20scope%20and%20applicability.%20In%20the%20PMO%20formulation%2C%20not%20only%20should%20the%20complete%20intake%20of%20the%20year%20be%20short-service%20based%2C%20but%20it%20would%20also%20apply%20to%20all%20three%20services%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHaving%20become%20a%20tri-service%20matter%2C%20it%20now%20fell%20on%20the%20CDS%2C%20General%20Bipin%20Rawat%2C%20to%20take%20the%20proposal%20forward%2C%20albeit%20with%20the%20Army%20remaining%20the%20lead%20service.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%2C%20in%20the%20Army%2C%20were%20taken%20by%20surprise%20by%20this%20turn%20of%20events%2C%20but%20for%20the%20Navy%20and%20Air%20Force%2C%20it%20came%20like%20a%20bolt%20from%20the%20blue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fagnipath-scheme-job-destruction-creation-modi-government%5C%22%3EAgnipath%20Is%20a%20Marketing%20Trick%20in%20Which%20Job%20Destruction