0and%20its%20second%20largest%20city%2C%20Kharkiv%2C%20came%20under%20attack%20from%20drones.%20Over%20100%20people%20were%20injured%20and%20at%20least%20five%20others%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20day%20later%2C%20Russian%20officials%20reported%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2024%2F1%2F3%2Fukraine-targets-russian-border-regions-in-retaliatory-strikes%5C%22%3EUkrainian%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20targeted%20cities%20in%20southern%20Russia%20and%20the%20Crimean%20peninsula%2C%20killing%20dozens%20of%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20foreign%20minister%20Dmytro%20Kuleba%20and%20his%20Indian%20counterpart%20S.%20Jaishankar%20spoke%20on%20Wednesday%20about%20%E2%80%9CRussia%E2%80%99s%20recent%20escalation%20of%20terror%20and%20mass%20air%20attacks%2C%20which%20caused%20civilian%20suffering%20and%20destruction%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuleba%20also%20raised%20Ukraine%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cvision%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20global%20summit%20of%20leaders%20to%20deliberate%20on%20peace%20proposals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMy%20first%20call%20in%202024%20was%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDrSJaishankar%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40DrSJaishankar%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Ukrainian-Indian%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20informed%20my%20counterpart%20of%20Russia%E2%80%99s%20recent%20escalation%20of%20terror%20and%20mass%20air%20attacks%2C%20which%20caused%20civilian%20suffering%20and%20destruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20discussed%20further%20cooperation%20on%20the%20Peace%20Formula.%20In%20this%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dmytro%20Kuleba%20(%40DmytroKuleba)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDmytroKuleba%2Fstatus%2F1742484990313541899%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe