l%5C%22%3Eheld%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20all%20the%20imports%20were%20genuine.%20It%20concluded%20that%20the%20value%20declared%20was%20correct%20and%20was%20not%20required%20to%20be%20re-determined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20Deloitte%E2%80%99s%20inability%20to%20determine%20whether%20Howe%20should%20be%20labelled%20a%20related%20party%20was%20why%20the%20auditor%20raised%20red%20flags%20about%20payments%20by%20Adani%E2%80%99s%20ports%20company%20to%20the%20contracting%20firm%20in%20May%2C%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindenburg%20Research%20directly%20called%20out%20PMC%2C%20in%20its%20report%2C%20alleging%20it%20was%20an%20Adani%20related%20party%20%E2%80%9Cused%20to%20suck%20money%20out%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%E2%80%99s%20publicly%20listed%20entities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsebi-concealed-dri-letter-on-stock-market-manipulation-by-adani-group-in-2014-petitioner-to-sc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESEBI%20%E2%80%98Concealed%E2%80%99%20DRI%20Letter%20on%20Stock%20Market%20Manipulation%20by%20Adani%20Group%20in%202014%3A%20Petitioner%20to%20SC%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20(%3Cstrong%3ESeptember%2012%2C%202023)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20September%201%2C%202023%2C%20the%20Organised%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%20(OCCRP)%2C%20a%20group%20of%20investigative%20reporters%2C%20found%20that%20the%20markets%20regulator%20had%20known%20about%20the%20stock%20manipulation%20allegations%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Farticle%2F1055231%2Fsebi-knew-about-allegations-against-adani-group-since-2014-letter-shows%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EScroll.in%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20a%20petitioner%20in%20the%20Adani-Hindenburg%20case%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20filed%20an%20affidavit%2C%20accusing%20SEBI%20of%20%E2%80%9Cconcealing%E2%80%9D%20an%20alert%20it%20received%20from%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%20in%20January%202014%20about%20stock%20market%20manipulation%20by%20the%20Adani%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20claimed%20the%20DRI%20sent%20a%20letter%20to%20then%20SEBI%20chairperson%2C%20U.K.%20Sinha%2C%20on%20January%2031%2C%202014%2C%20alerting%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthere%20may%20be%20stock%20market%20manipulation%20being%20committed%20by%20the%20Adani%20group%20of%20companies%20using%20the%20money%20siphoned%20off%20through%20overvaluation%20in%20the%20import%20of%20power%20equipment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20DRI%20had%20sent%20a%20CD%2C%20containing%20evidence%20of%20siphoning%20of%20Rs%202%2C323%20crore%20and%20notes%20on%20the%20case%20being%20probed%20by%20the%20anti-smuggling%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20OCCRP%20report%20was%20also%20shared%20with%3Cem%3E%C2%A0The%20Guardian%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0and%C2%A0%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20affidavit%20also%20highlighted%20that%20Sinha%2C%20the%20then%20SEBI%20head%2C%20currently%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbctv18.com%2Fbusiness%2Fcompanies%2Fndtv-appoints-former-sebi-chairman-uk-sinha-as-non-executive-chairman-16279441.htm%5C%22%3Eserves%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0as%20the%20non-executive%20director%20of%20NDTV%2C%20which%20was%20acquired%20by%20the%20Adani%20group%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-coal-imports-over-pricing-customers-overcharged-fuel-ft%5C%22%3EOverpricing%20of%20Coal%20Imports%20by%20Adani%20Group%20Led%20to%20Higher%20Profits%2C%20Customers%20Overcharged%20for%20Fuel%3A%20FT%3C%2Fa%3E%20(October%2012%2C%202023)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Times%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0in%20a%20detailed%20investigation%2C%20titled%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ft.com%2Fcontent%2F7aadb3d7-4a03-44ba-a01e-8ddd8bce29ed%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20mystery%20of%20the%20Adan