reds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20worth%20of%20the%20Adani%20Group%20conglomerate%E2%80%99s%20public%20stock%2C%20possibly%20in%20violation%20of%20Indian%20securities%20law.%20A%20forensic%20analysis%20of%20Mangnale%E2%80%99s%20phone%2C%20conducted%20by%20Amnesty%20International%20and%20shared%20withThe%20Washington%20Post%2C%20found%20that%20within%2024%20hours%20of%20that%20inquiry%2C%20an%20attacker%20infiltrated%20the%20device%20and%20planted%C2%A0Pegasus%2C%20the%20notorious%20spyware%C2%A0that%20was%20developed%20by%20Israeli%20company%20NSO%20Groupand%20that%20NSO%20says%20is%20sold%20only%20to%20governments.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmnesty%20said%20its%20Security%20Lab%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20observed%20indications%20of%20renewed%20Pegasus%20spyware%20threats%20towards%20individuals%20in%20India%20during%20a%20regular%20technical%20monitoring%20exercise%20in%20June%202023%2C%20a%20number%20of%20months%20after%20media%20reported%20that%20the%20Indian%20government%20was%20seeking%20to%20procure%20a%20new%20commercial%20spyware%20system.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Apple%20issued%20threat%20notifications%20globally%20to%20iPhone%20users%20who%20may%20have%20been%20targeted%20by%20%E2%80%9Cstate-sponsored%20attackers%E2%80%9D%2C%20Varadarajan%2C%20Mangnale%20and%20a%20number%20of%20other%20journalists%20and%20opposition%20politicians%20in%20India%20received%20the%20notifications.%20Among%20those%20who%20went%20public%20at%20the%20time%20were%20Mahua%20Moitra%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%2C%20a%20prominent%20critic%20of%20the%20Adani%20group%2C%20and%20Ravi%20Nair%2C%20a%20journalist%20with%20OCCRP%20who%20was%20working%20on%20an%20Adani%20story%20with%20Mangnale.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704281412000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F03%2F16194940%2Fadanis.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbusiness%2Fadani-hindenburg-case-vinod-adani-to-pegasus-targeting-on-